  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/0822732a7bbd22feeb4ad578706b7496.avif?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“HERADÔNIA” is a psychological horror game.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>STORY</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Julia is a simple woman who lives with her husband and daughter in the city of Heradônia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After arriving home and realizing her husband had left town for work, she notices her house has been ransacked. Thus, Julia begins a journey in search of her daughter, a journey that will force her to confront her deepest secrets—the ones she tried hardest to hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/a9528235427a5deb36425da2bbeb82dc.webp?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-person horror:</strong> Play as Julia, a simple woman living with her husband and daughter in the city of Heradônia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environments:</strong> The world of Heradônia is set in the 2000s. Explore city environments like the school and the city hospital.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/a9528235427a5deb36425da2bbeb82dc.webp?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Item collection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle solving</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/a9528235427a5deb36425da2bbeb82dc.webp?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=4 /></span></p>",
